  "detailed_description": "《心动满屋》是一款恋综形式的动态真人互动影像作品。你将在此化身恋综嘉宾，与六位性格独特、魅力四溢的美女嘉宾浪漫邂逅，一同开启甜蜜又刺激的同居生活。<br>在游戏中，你将成为恋综节目的主角，决定着爱情的走向。无论是与嘉宾温馨甜蜜牵手，还是经历戏剧性的爱恨情仇，都取决于你的选择。你可以专注于一段感情，也可以成为海王撩遍全场，甚至成为恋综节目的人气王。《心动满屋》让你尽情体验恋爱的多种可能性，重塑你的爱情观念，开启属于你的恋爱冒险之旅。<br><br>高傲的艺术世家小才女：刘希樾<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/b2954fde3683d3642e48a2f79b86ad5d.poster.avif?t=1732260543\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/b2954fde3683d3642e48a2f79b86ad5d.webm?t=1732260543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/b2954fde3683d3642e48a2f79b86ad5d.mp4?t=1732260543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>知性成熟的电台主持人：郑妍<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/8ab4cf4a742987b04c864bd9f7882a79.poster.avif?t=1732260543\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/8ab4cf4a742987b04c864bd9f7882a79.webm?t=1732260543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/8ab4cf4a742987b04c864bd9f7882a79.mp4?t=1732260543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>甜美单纯的学生妹：甜甜<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/48ce9e3ec50b93170ab43276b9c1d60d.poster.avif?t=1732260543\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002930/extras/48ce9e3ec50b93170ab43276b9c1d60d.webm?t=1732260543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"h